2. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking): The paper is focused on the design of a wireless communication system, which falls under the domain of communication and networking. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a novel concept for the design of a collaborative unitary space-time block code, which can be considered as a system design problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses the design of a coding scheme for wireless communication, which can be related to multimedia applications. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with the design of a wireless communication system, which can be considered as a networking and internet architecture problem.
